This is a Next.js v15 app using app router. Using react-query with prefetching and query hydration.

Owner: organization or user in github owning repositories. ('jonator' in repository 'jonator/swarm')
Repository: repository in github owned by owner ('swarm' in 'jonator/swarm')
Agents: currently, agents are ephemeral and their messages are not persisted. So only currently working agents are displayed or available.
* [owner]
    / Overview: lists repositories and projects, each with an indicator of the number of agents active
    /~/ [agents]: lists agents across all repositories associated with owner
    /~/ [settings]: manage settings for the owner (user or org)
    / [repository]
        / Overview: lists active agents
        / [agents]: lists agents associated with repository
        / [messages]: lists messages from agents associated with repository
        / [settings]: manage settings for repository
